platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In Baba Is You’s brilliant puzzles, rules are meant to be broken—or at least rewritten. Brick wall standing between you and the victory flag? Shift blocks of text to form phrases that change the way the world works. With a few moves, “wall is stop” becomes “wall is push”—and success is suddenly within your grasp. You’ll marvel as the game responds instantly to your newly created laws. Spell yourself into a corner? Just rewind and retrace your steps. Baba is you, and you’re in charge.
